[SN]TITLE[SN]
Cash calendar - tips for August

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Summer spending can push people into financial trouble for the rest of the year so now is a good time to check the budget, an expert says.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
1 August 2016 Last updated at 00:22 BST
The BBC News website asked the independent Money Advice Service to deliver a calendar of month-by-month tips for those trying to keep their personal finances in order.
Andy Webb, from the service, says reviewing your finances can be as easy as picking up a piece of paper and a pen.
